9
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:56,656
These fair-weather folks

10
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:58,576
used to treat me like their savior,

11
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,776
but the moment things turned,

12
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:01,120
