13
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:02,880
Dad,

14
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,520
Ye Ying and Huo Xiao

15
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:06,296
raided the illicit warehouse,

16
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:07,920
