30
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,360
Can we outrun this?

31
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:36,776
Besides, making me give up

32
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,136
what I've plotted half my life,

33
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,920
what I've slaved to build,

34
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,520
