The real show hasn't started.

80
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,720
So arrogant usually.

81
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,200
What a coward.

82
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,840
Other places aren't safe anymore.

83
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,560
Only here.

84
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,696
Song Pa's influence can't reach here.

85
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:46,016
I've got people guarding all exits outside.

86
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,736
But there are many new faces.

87
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,240
Probably Song Pa's spies.

88
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,320
They found us this fast.

89
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,200
You've got two choices now.

90
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,440
Either

91
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,856
