94
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,256
You're the reason I'm in this mess.

95
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,696
And now you want to
climb over my back?

96
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,040
Dream on!

97
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,457
And you,

98
00:05:13,481 --> 00:05:14,816
you're just like Ye Hong.

99
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,136
Can't appreciate a peaceful life,

100
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,336
but had to dig into the dirty business,

101
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,240
