111
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:53,840
A hundred million.

112
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,920
A hundred million.

113
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,480
Give me a hundred million.

114
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,200
Then send me abroad.

115
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,680
In Song Pa's eyes,

116
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,520
