119
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,200
Bargaining with me?

120
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,880
Are you crazy?

121
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,736
If you insist on walking the path to death,

122
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,200
