128
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,880
Rong.

129
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,080
What are you doing?

130
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:50,936
What are you doing?

131
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,256
What are you all doing?

132
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,280
Let me go!

133
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,600
I said let me go!

134
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,120
I see you're acting more

135
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,480
