151
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,056
This isn't just about
revenge for the gang.

152
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,080
It's personal too.

153
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,616
Every one of us in Qingyun Gang,

154
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,176
