with Song Pa.

158
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,720
But a few of our guys
got ambushed and hurt.

159
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,936
Go treat your wounds first.

160
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:24,960
Okay.

161
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,600
To make sure nothing goes wrong.

162
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,297
I'll take Jiang Meng

163
00:08:31,321 --> 00:08:32,856
and head out of the city from the north.

164
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:33,537
At that time,

165
00:08:33,561 --> 00:08:35,216
