170
00:08:39,161 --> 00:08:40,360
It's relatively safe.

171
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,000
Everyone, get ready.

172
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,480
Yes.

173
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,000
Be careful.

174
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,416
You still owe me a lot of promises.

175
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,000
I'm not letting anything happen to you.

176
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,880
Relax.

177
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,800
I'm not that easy to kill.

178
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,936
What are you staring at?

179
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,960
Get back to work.

180
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,960
Useless bunch!

181
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,057
No matter what happens.

182
00:09:39,081 --> 00:09:40,736
Get Jiang Meng

183
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,040
and all that evidence back!

184
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,520
Dad.

185
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,297
Right now,

186
00:09:46,321 --> 00:09:47,880
