187
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,360
I'm afraid

188
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,856
they won't be easy to take down.

189
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,080
Push me to the edge.

190
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,040
Then a lot of people
will go down with me.

191
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,496
Use all connections,

192
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,656
all strength.

193
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:58,136
No matter what it takes,

194
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,400
we can't let them survive this!

195
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:00,640
Yes.

196
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,600
Hear that?

197
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,240
Yes, yes.

198
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,240
Prosecutor,

199
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,520
this is the witness
in the Song family gang crime case.

200
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,217
I formally

201
00:10:16,241 --> 00:10:17,560
