202
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:18,880
Okay, Inspector Huo.

203
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,720
It's finally over.

204
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:42,696
Why?

205
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,920
We're colleagues.

206
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:46,120
Why help Song Pa silence him?

207
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,360
Inspector Huo.

208
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:55,056
Song Pa took my family hostage.

209
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,576
He said if I didn't kill Jiang Meng by 3,

210
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,800
