211
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,360
I didn't have a choice.

212
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,480
Take him away.

213
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,000
Yes, sir.

214
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:12,640
Wait.

215
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,960
No.

216
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,376
No...

217
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,400
Move!

218
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,840
- Move!
- No.

219
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,840
[Huo Xiao]

220
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,016
I shook off the killers

221
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,216
