222
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,016
Jiang Meng is dead.

223
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:35,936
There's a mole.

224
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,960
Go, now!

225
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,600
Ye Ying.

226
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,360
Ye Ying!

227
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,696
What a pity.

228
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,760
You almost made it.

229
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,216
But with Jiang Meng dead,

230
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,160
