231
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,216
Now

232
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,200
it's my turn to strike back.

233
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:21,080
The best strategy is to retreat.

234
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,600
Time to slip away first.

235
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:38,280
Ye Ying.

236
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:41,120
Didn't expect to
end up in my hands, huh?

237
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,160
This is called.

238
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,720
"Wait for the prey to come to you."

239
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,040
So what do you want?

240
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,360
To kill me?

241
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:52,136
If you fell into my dad's hands,

242
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,360
you might be dead.

243
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,760
But in mine,

244
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,777
I'm willing to

245
00:12:56,801 --> 00:12:58,536
take the risk

246
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,457
to take you

247
00:12:59,481 --> 00:13:01,240
far away.

248
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:13,600
The old me might've said no,

249
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,680
but now it's different.

250
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,200
But

251
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,600
how will you protect me?

252
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:25,216
As long as you obediently follow me

253
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,976
and do as I say,

254
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,040
I'd never let anything happen to you.

255
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:42,720
Then I better show you what I've got.

256
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,760
So kinky.

257
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,976
Quite a few tricks, huh?

258
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,160
Why pretend to be a pure saint before?

259
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,480
See.

260
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:55,640
Showing your wild side at last.

261
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,680
The exciting part

262
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,160
