263
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,240
Remember your masterpiece?

264
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,456
You're not Ye Ying.

265
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,656
You're An Ning!

266
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:19,920
You're alive.

267
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,320
You shameless woman.

268
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,000
You dared to lie to me!

269
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:34,416
I just love your unrepentant ways.

270
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,600
Otherwise, I might've hesitated.

