♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

278
00:15:35,780 --> 00:15:39,736
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

279
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:43,336
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

280
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:46,296
